ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectAppointment of the Joint Auditor of the wholly-owned subsidiaries of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board
PrecisOrder Appointing (a) an AUDITOR for each of the wholly-owned subsidiaries of the PUBLIC SECTOR PENSION INVESTMENT BOARD for their respective years ending between January 1, 2019 and March 31, 2020; and (b) the AUDITOR GENERAL OF CANADA as JOINT AUDITOR of each of the wholly-owned subsidiaries for their respective fiscal years ending between January 1, 2019 and March 31, 2020.
